{"tid":368754,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"〈心事〉人大左先知自己屋企窮","createTime":"2017-08-21T18:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T17:45:00.000Z","uid":71198,"like":8,"dislike":137,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4854e0715650f59a73fe1d486960d3e3cdfef25e","tid":368754,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:55:39.000Z","msg":"出嚟見識多左發現原來自己屋企原來係屬於窮<br />\n最近識左個屋企三千幾呎，有私人司機<br />\n幾個鋪位，就咁睇已經幾億身家<br />\n一億如果計四厘回報一年都有400萬<br />\n三億一年咪千幾萬？<br />\n一個月咪唔駛做都有百幾萬？<br />\n一比較就好失落，人地就三千幾呎，<br />\n我住果到就先得千零呎，仲要唔係新樓<br />\n我坐飛機都淨係坐商務，廿幾歲仔都未坐過頭等<br />\n我以前覺得屋企都算唔錯，依家有半億多啲資產<br />\n但係原來人外有人，天外有天"},{"pid":"7c6c12fa064369cf7e3cdc7101b7d67968b0d879","tid":368754,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:00:57.000Z","msg":"咁你真係好窮喎～"},{"pid":"fc4ce5e521806c90f6528cda13f4c5cf4a391f3c","tid":368754,"uid":120821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你真係好窮喎～</blockquote><br />\n係囉，你咁窮，替你擔心~"},{"pid":"91e65cb847a07e4c3ac390785f499f3ec2da8a90","tid":368754,"uid":31733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:14:48.000Z","msg":"搏dislike <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有半億身家背景既人，<br />\n你以為隨便街就搵到個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe53f1adf7a1618f4d8e22aebd7038dd1ba434b","tid":368754,"uid":71198,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:16:37.000Z","msg":"負評即係點？<br />\n我講嘅係夜半心事，亦都係依半年失眠嘅主因<br />\n人地啲仔唔駛點做，揸架車翻公司點下人做嘢，溝下女同事，<br />\n個個月老豆出十幾萬糧俾佢<br />\n我就坐的士翻工，再唔係就uber，<br />\n做到狗咁，雞碎咁多糧<br />\n人地旅行就頭等，鐘意幾時飛就幾時飛<br />\n我就頂盡得商務，仲要唔係隨時鐘意幾時走都得"},{"pid":"1aaddf5c492c75b9cac1d30222c988f13f963088","tid":368754,"uid":71198,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搏dislike <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有半億身家背景既人，<br />\n你以為隨便街就搵到個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n何文田求其一間新樓都過千五萬<br />\n有啲大單位二三千，<br />\n大把人一筆過落仔女名買，<br />\n你唔知姐"},{"pid":"35e04f65c100446a251d16b1ab5f41ee65babb20","tid":368754,"uid":71198,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:22:40.000Z","msg":"職業無分貴賤，但係人係有高低之分<br />\n我只係唔甘心姐"},{"pid":"e14c06a7fd302456ef30ba07a2702a577a87f60f","tid":368754,"uid":129866,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:22:45.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲人應該有自力更生嘅條件仲係到為唔係你賺翻黎嘅錢自卑?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醜唔醜啲..."},{"pid":"727449c6a00033ffe25da4e057b40ed245d9494b","tid":368754,"uid":71198,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:25:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廿幾歲人應該有自力更生嘅條件仲係到為唔係你賺翻黎嘅錢自卑?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醜唔醜啲...</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦，何鴻燊個仔唔係佢老豆有<br />\n憑佢自己本事，陳瀅會俾佢屌？<br />\n身力更生，正常人都有<br />\n我依家講緊係父幹同埋家底嘅比較"},{"pid":"bccb2c7b8c138930c7d945102918a2181e2bcb1e","tid":368754,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:25:27.000Z","msg":"老豆係日本買左層樓俾我<br />\n又如何 人地收432 park ave<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c100fa4cff4506820d360864150f307141232a9","tid":368754,"uid":81421,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:25:46.000Z","msg":"半億其實好少, 依家香港大把過億, 冇三億以上都唔算有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 2億幾"},{"pid":"2288d694b4d86c693566f59337668580036d6834","tid":368754,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:26:27.000Z","msg":"自己有半億 再周圍同人講人地有幾十億身家老豆照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" c